  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multi-center registry study. The investigators will include 10,000 patients with
      confirmed acute ischemic stroke in China. The aim of the study is to survey current treatment
      situation in China and compare the effectiveness and safety between different intervention
      regimens.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Stroke is a common disease in China. Compared to western countries, there are many treatment
      regimens used in clinical practice in China. But their treatment effects are not well
      validated. The aim of the study is to survey current treatment situation in China and compare
      the effectiveness and safety between different intervention regimens.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
